00:55:19,881 --> 00:55:22,441
it's like he can't shut Jason back down.

812
00:55:22,483 --> 00:55:24,110
Wait a minute.

813
00:55:24,152 --> 00:55:27,178
Freddy died by fire, Jason by water.

814
00:55:27,221 --> 00:55:29,280
How can we use that?

815
00:55:29,324 --> 00:55:32,122
I think we should concentrate on Jason first.

816
00:55:32,160 --> 00:55:33,855
But I thought we decided...

817
00:55:33,895 --> 00:55:35,590
that Freddy was the one pulling the strings.

818
00:55:35,630 --> 00:55:38,064
Shouldn't we go after him first?

819
00:55:38,099 --> 00:55:40,727
I don't know, maybe what we need to do is...

820
00:55:40,768 --> 00:55:43,362
to offer Freddy a sacrifice.

821
00:55:43,404 --> 00:55:44,962
Yeah, yeah, totally.

822
00:55:45,006 --> 00:55:48,237
Like a virgin, right? Someone pure.

823
00:55:53,648 --> 00:55:56,048
Dude, don't look at me.

824
00:55:56,084 --> 00:55:58,552
Even if you pay for it, it still counts.

825
00:55:58,586 --> 00:56:00,645
Oh, come on.

826
00:56:00,688 --> 00:56:03,486
Look, we all know who the real virgin is here.

827
00:56:03,524 --> 00:56:06,186
-Kia! -Oh, come on, Lori.

828
00:56:06,227 --> 00:56:08,024
I know you never made it with Will.

829
00:56:08,062 --> 00:56:12,863
Why would he want to when he can fuck somebody like me?

830
00:56:18,306 --> 00:56:19,898
Let's tie the bitch up.

831
00:56:22,877 --> 00:56:24,868
What?

832
00:56:27,315 --> 00:56:29,681
Don't worry, angel.

833
00:56:29,717 --> 00:56:31,378
