834
00:56:31,419 --> 00:56:33,887
Come on, give daddy a kiss.

835
00:56:38,593 --> 00:56:42,256
Your eyes say no-no...

836
00:56:42,296 --> 00:56:46,733
but my mouth says yes-yes.

837
00:56:51,172 --> 00:56:52,799
Lori, are you all right?

838
00:56:52,840 --> 00:56:54,000
You fell asleep.

839
00:57:02,116 --> 00:57:04,209
Oh, shit!

840
00:57:08,055 --> 00:57:10,046
I pulled that out of my dream.

841
00:57:10,091 --> 00:57:12,082
How is that possible?

842
00:57:12,126 --> 00:57:14,151
Anything is possible now!

843
00:57:14,195 --> 00:57:15,457
God, you just don't get it!

844
00:57:15,496 --> 00:57:17,623
Oh, God, y'all, two killers?

845
00:57:17,665 --> 00:57:19,565
We're not safe awake or asleep.

846
00:57:19,600 --> 00:57:21,431
It's not the sleep that's killing us...

847
00:57:21,469 --> 00:57:22,436
it's our dreams.

848
00:57:22,470 --> 00:57:25,132
At Westin, Mark and l never had dreams.

849
00:57:25,173 --> 00:57:27,903
Were you on any drugs?

850
00:57:27,942 --> 00:57:30,342
Yeah, but there's something called hypnocil.

851
00:57:30,378 --> 00:57:32,437
They never told us what it was for...

852
00:57:32,480 --> 00:57:34,505
but everyone there was taking it.

853
00:57:36,617 --> 00:57:39,245
Experimental drug...

854
00:57:39,287 --> 00:57:40,845
not even approved yet by the F.D.A.

855
00:57:40,888 --> 00:57:42,685
Oh, shit.

856
00:57:42,723 --> 00:57:46,625
Used for... suppression of dreams.

857
00:57:46,661 --> 00:57:50,153
We need those pills, enough for all of us.

858
00:57:50,198 --> 00:57:52,325
Can you get us back to Westin Hills?

859
00:58:12,653 --> 00:58:14,245
All right, this isn't it, guys.

860
00:58:14,288 --> 00:58:16,119
Come on, let's go.

861
00:58:16,157 --> 00:58:17,124
Hey, dude.

862
00:58:17,158 --> 00:58:18,489
Let's take a little J-break, huh?

863
00:58:18,526 --> 00:58:21,188
No, man. He's a cop.

864
00:58:21,229 --> 00:58:23,720
