865
00:58:23,764 --> 00:58:26,096
Hold up. Hang on a second.

866
00:58:26,133 --> 00:58:27,498
Fuck.

867
00:58:36,511 --> 00:58:38,308
That's better.

868
00:58:53,561 --> 00:58:55,722
