878
00:59:52,520 --> 00:59:54,886
Cool...yeah.

879
01:00:04,865 --> 01:00:07,493
What the fuck?

880
01:00:21,282 --> 01:00:22,681
Nice.

881
01:00:30,391 --> 01:00:32,188
Oh, yeah.

882
01:00:36,631 --> 01:00:38,326
