908
01:03:06,814 --> 01:03:09,112
We gotta go! Now! come on!

909
01:03:09,150 --> 01:03:11,812
Let me handle this, bitch.

910
01:03:11,852 --> 01:03:13,513
What?

911
01:03:15,055 --> 01:03:16,852
Come on, come on! OK, let's go!

912
01:03:18,225 --> 01:03:19,590
Let's go.

913
