917
01:03:31,405 --> 01:03:33,896
Go back where you belong!

918
01:03:44,585 --> 01:03:46,780
Fuck you!

919
01:03:48,556 --> 01:03:50,490
Linderman...

920
01:03:52,359 --> 01:03:55,726
These are my children, Jason.

921
01:03:55,763 --> 01:03:58,231
Go back where you belong.

922
01:04:10,544 --> 01:04:14,378
Jason...Jason.

923
