950
01:08:31,271 --> 01:08:34,638
Aww...how sweet.

951
01:08:35,776 --> 01:08:37,937
You ugly little shit.

952
01:08:37,978 --> 01:08:42,813
Now there's a face... only a mother could love!

953
01:08:45,152 --> 01:08:46,346
Yeah!

954
01:08:46,386 --> 01:08:48,286
Now we're getting somewhere.

955
01:08:48,322 --> 01:08:50,950
