958
01:09:51,852 --> 01:09:54,150
We're seriously running out of tranq here, guys.

959
01:09:54,188 --> 01:09:57,419
I got maybe one dose, plus enough for Lori.

960
01:09:57,457 --> 01:09:58,685
Well, we're almost there.

961
01:09:58,725 --> 01:10:00,124
Then I better get going.

962
01:10:00,160 --> 01:10:01,388
No, no, just...

963
01:10:06,433 --> 01:10:07,764
I don't want you to go.

964
01:10:07,801 --> 01:10:09,325
I'm coming back.

965
01:10:09,369 --> 01:10:12,031
Just give me fifteen minutes, then wake me up.

966
01:10:12,072 --> 01:10:14,302
I'll bring that bastard Freddy back through.

967
01:10:14,341 --> 01:10:17,071
Just make sure Jason's waiting for him.

968
01:10:21,715 --> 01:10:24,843
Now I lay me down to sleep.

969
01:10:46,406 --> 01:10:50,706
Freak show! Freak show! Freak show! Freak show!

970
01:10:50,744 --> 01:10:52,234
Bull's-eye!

971
01:10:56,350 --> 01:10:58,375
Freak show! Freak show! Freak show!

972
01:10:58,418 --> 01:10:59,817
Try this on!

973
01:11:01,021 --> 01:11:04,115
Freak show! Freak show! Freak show!

974
01:11:08,028 --> 01:11:09,461
Stupid!

975
01:11:12,766 --> 01:11:14,734
Aren't you gonna help the kid?!

976
01:11:14,768 --> 01:11:17,293
Can't you see I'm busy here?

977
01:11:17,337 --> 01:11:18,770
You mean you're not coming?

978
01:11:21,708 --> 01:11:24,973
It's not my fault this bitch is dead on her feet.

979
01:11:33,787 --> 01:11:35,379
It's been five minutes.

980
01:11:35,422 --> 01:11:37,617
Well, that was the last of the tranq, OK? We're out.

981
01:11:37,658 --> 01:11:39,592
Calm down, OK? Just relax!

982
01:11:53,373 --> 01:11:55,307
Heeeeelp!

983
01:11:55,342 --> 01:11:58,971
Wait! Give me your hand!

984
01:11:59,012 --> 01:12:01,776
Give me your hand!

985
01:12:03,283 --> 01:12:04,375
Help!

986
01:12:04,418 --> 01:12:06,682
Jason?

987
01:12:06,720 --> 01:12:08,483
Jason Vorhees?

988
01:12:19,166 --> 01:12:21,134
Y'all...y'all...

989
01:12:21,168 --> 01:12:22,192
Y'all, something's wrong.

990
01:12:22,235 --> 01:12:23,429
It's like he's drowning or something.

991
01:12:23,470 --> 01:12:24,835
Freddy must be killing him.

992
01:12:24,871 --> 01:12:25,838
We need him alive!

993
01:12:25,872 --> 01:12:26,964
Dude, what do you want me to do...

994
01:12:27,007 --> 01:12:29,475
Iike, give him mouth-to-mouth or something?

995
01:12:37,217 --> 01:12:39,048
Hell no. Why are you--

996
01:12:39,086 --> 01:12:41,554
No! No, I'm not gonna do that. No!

997
01:12:41,588 --> 01:12:42,850
Kia, look, I would do it myself...

998
01:12:42,889 --> 01:12:44,584
but I've had asthma since I was six, OK?

999
01:12:44,624 --> 01:12:46,091
I don't have the lung power.

1000
01:12:46,126 --> 01:12:47,559
No.

1001
01:12:47,594 --> 01:12:49,926
Kia, he has asthma!

1002
01:12:49,963 --> 01:12:52,488
Ooh! Ooh...

1003
01:12:53,734 --> 01:12:55,429
Look, you can do this, OK?

1004
01:12:55,469 --> 01:12:56,595
You can do this. You just--

1005
01:12:56,636 --> 01:13:00,367
Shut up! You're not the one that has to do this.

1006
01:13:00,407 --> 01:13:01,396
I know, but l--

1007
01:13:01,441 --> 01:13:02,806
Shut up!

1008
01:13:05,879 --> 01:13:07,938
Oh, my God.

1009
01:13:09,883 --> 01:13:12,351
Ohh, God!

1010
01:13:17,591 --> 01:13:19,252
Oh, man.

1011
01:13:19,292 --> 01:13:22,284
Oh, shit. Oh, shit.

1012
01:13:45,952 --> 01:13:48,079
You!

1013
01:14:02,269 --> 01:14:03,998
What's wrong, Lori?

1014
01:14:04,037 --> 01:14:05,937
Miss your wake-up call?

1015
01:14:08,508 --> 01:14:10,669
Wake me up! I got him! I got him!

1016
01:14:15,782 --> 01:14:17,909
No!

1017
01:14:17,951 --> 01:14:18,975
Lori, come on! Wake up!

1018
01:14:19,019 --> 01:14:20,680
Lori, wake up, please!

1019
01:14:20,720 --> 01:14:22,119
Look!

1020
01:14:22,155 --> 01:14:23,645
Guys, look.

1021
01:14:25,358 --> 01:14:26,450
We're almost there.

1022
01:14:26,493 --> 01:14:29,291
Help me. Come on. We gotta get her up.

1023
01:14:30,564 --> 01:14:32,623
Come on. Start running. Start running.

1024
01:14:32,666 --> 01:14:34,566
Wake me up!

1025
01:14:36,303 --> 01:14:37,964
Daddy, don't!

1026
01:15:04,331 --> 01:15:06,856
Daddy! No, daddy, don't!

1027
01:15:06,900 --> 01:15:08,731
Freddy! It was you!

1028
01:15:09,769 --> 01:15:10,861
I've always had a thing...

1029
01:15:10,904 --> 01:15:13,702
for the whores that live in this house.

1030
01:15:23,884 --> 01:15:24,908
Lori, wake up!

1031
01:15:27,854 --> 01:15:29,185
Oh, shit.

1032
01:15:34,127 --> 01:15:35,560
It's him. He's here.

1033
01:15:35,595 --> 01:15:37,187
Lori, come on! You gotta wake up!

1034
01:15:41,935 --> 01:15:43,562
Oh, yes.

1035
01:15:48,642 --> 01:15:50,610
My God!

1036
01:15:52,812 --> 01:15:54,404
Come on, Lori, wake up!

1037
01:15:54,447 --> 01:15:56,039
Lori, please. Wake up!

1038
01:15:56,082 --> 01:15:57,674
Lori, please. Lori, please.

1039
01:16:04,124 --> 01:16:05,148
Go! Go, go, go!

1040
01:16:08,194 --> 01:16:09,491
Lori!

1041
01:16:14,734 --> 01:16:16,759
Oh, you fuckin' asshole!

1042
01:16:16,803 --> 01:16:17,929
Goddamn it!

1043
01:16:21,975 --> 01:16:25,001
Welcome to my world, bitch.

1044
01:16:27,247 --> 01:16:29,977
I should warn you, princess...

1045
01:16:30,016 --> 01:16:32,610
the first time tends to get a little...

1046
01:16:33,853 --> 01:16:35,980
messy.

1047
01:16:53,006 --> 01:16:53,995
Get away from her!

1048
01:17:01,548 --> 01:17:02,480
Linderman.

1049
01:17:09,589 --> 01:17:10,851
Oh! Oh, no!

1050
01:17:18,565 --> 01:17:21,227
Die, you little bitch.

1051
01:18:15,622 --> 01:18:18,022
Jesus, Linderman. You--you're really hurt.

1052
01:18:18,058 --> 01:18:19,889
No. No, no, no. Don't worry about me.

1053
01:18:19,926 --> 01:18:21,052
Just a scratch.

1054
01:18:21,094 --> 01:18:22,220
Just go get help, OK?

1055
01:18:22,262 --> 01:18:24,287
What? You don't think--

1056
01:18:24,330 --> 01:18:26,127
Look, I'm just gonna rest here a minute.

1057
01:18:26,166 --> 01:18:28,464
-Linderman-- -I'm fine, Kia.

1058
01:18:28,501 --> 01:18:29,763
Really. Now get out of here.

1059
01:18:29,803 --> 01:18:31,327
-Go get help. -But you--

1060
01:18:31,371 --> 01:18:32,895
Just go.

1061
01:18:33,973 --> 01:18:37,465
OK, but I'm gonna be back as soon as I can.

1062
01:19:17,450 --> 01:19:18,712
Lori!

1063
01:19:18,752 --> 01:19:21,084
Think you're so smart, huh, bitch?

1064
01:19:22,555 --> 01:19:23,920
Freddy!

1065
01:19:33,466 --> 01:19:35,559
How sweet...

1066
01:19:35,602 --> 01:19:37,502
dark meat.

1067
01:19:37,537 --> 01:19:40,404
-No! Kia! -Let's go!

1068
01:19:40,440 --> 01:19:41,907
Nooo!

1069
01:19:41,941 --> 01:19:44,273
So you're the one everyone's afraid of?

1070
01:19:46,546 --> 01:19:48,571
Tell me something.

1071
01:19:48,615 --> 01:19:50,310
What kind of faggot...

1072
01:19:50,350 --> 01:19:52,978
runs around in a Christmas sweater?

1073
01:19:54,354 --> 01:19:56,686
I mean, come on. Get real.

1074
01:19:56,723 --> 01:19:58,384
You're not even scary.

1075
01:19:58,424 --> 01:20:00,187
You're not even scary.

1076
01:20:00,226 --> 01:20:04,060
And let's talk about the butter knives.

1077
01:20:04,097 --> 01:20:05,894
What is with the butter knives?

1078
01:20:05,932 --> 01:20:09,026
You trying to compensate for something?

1079
01:20:09,068 --> 01:20:10,535
Maybe coming up a little short there...

1080
01:20:10,570 --> 01:20:13,630
between the legs, Mr. Krueger?

1081
01:20:13,673 --> 01:20:14,833
Hmm.

1082
01:20:14,874 --> 01:20:18,401
I mean, you got these teensy-weensy little things...

1083
01:20:18,444 --> 01:20:23,882
and Jason has got this big ol' thing that's like...

1084
01:20:32,926 --> 01:20:33,915
Kia!

1085
01:20:33,960 --> 01:20:35,860
-No! No! -Come on!

1086
01:20:41,234 --> 01:20:42,223
Come on, Lori. Let's go.

1087
01:20:42,268 --> 01:20:43,292
We can't help her anymore.

1088
01:20:43,336 --> 01:20:44,963
No! I'm staying!

1089
01:20:45,004 --> 01:20:47,564
Are you crazy? You got what you wanted.

1090
01:20:47,607 --> 01:20:49,438
You pulled Freddy out, and now he's fighting Jason.

1091
01:20:49,475 --> 01:20:50,669
Come on! What more do you want?

1092
01:20:50,710 --> 01:20:52,575
He killed my mother, Will!

1093
01:20:52,612 --> 01:20:53,977
It was Freddy.

1094
01:20:54,013 --> 01:20:56,345
My dad covered it up to protect me.

1095
01:20:56,382 --> 01:20:57,349
He didn't do it.

1096
01:20:57,383 --> 01:20:58,907
Look, he has taken everything from us!

1097
01:20:58,952 --> 01:21:01,284
He has ruined both of our pasts...

1098
01:21:01,321 --> 01:21:04,688
and I am not leaving until I see him die!

1099
01:21:33,419 --> 01:21:35,250
Man the torpedoes.

1100
01:21:59,379 --> 01:22:01,006
Hey, asshole!

1101
01:22:02,548 --> 01:22:04,175
Up here!

1102
01:22:10,790 --> 01:22:12,587
Aha!

1103
01:22:29,676 --> 01:22:31,041
Yeah.

1104
01:22:41,721 --> 01:22:43,552
Ah, give me a break.

1105
01:23:09,282 --> 01:23:10,715
Oh, no.

1106
01:23:10,750 --> 01:23:14,709
Ohh, noooo!

1107
01:24:38,805 --> 01:24:40,739
Lori, get the tanks!

1108
01:24:44,477 --> 01:24:45,739
Give it up!

1109
01:25:13,039 --> 01:25:14,597
Freddy!

1110
01:25:16,209 --> 01:25:17,540
Go to hell!

1111
01:27:06,652 --> 01:27:08,586
It's OK. It's OK.

1112
01:27:39,986 --> 01:27:41,613
You...

1113
01:28:13,452 --> 01:28:16,353
Welcome to my world, bitch!
